'''NGC 1222''' 是[[波江座|波江座]]的一個[[透鏡狀星系|透鏡狀星系]]。該星系距離地球約1.09億光年<ref name=Sci-News>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/hubble-ngc-1222-04342.html |title=Hubble Space Telescope Observes NGC 1222 |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2017-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105020023/http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/hubble-ngc-1222-04342.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

NGC 1222是快速形成恆星中的[[星暴星系|星暴星系]]<ref>[http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/objsearch?objname=NGC+1222&extend=no&hconst=73&omegam=0.27&omegav=0.73&corr_z=1&out_csys=Equatorial&out_equinox=J2000.0&obj_sort=RA+or+Longitude&of=pre_text&zv_breaker=30000.0&list_limit=5&img_stamp=YES NED results for object NGC 1222.] {{Wayback|url=http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/objsearch?objname=NGC+1222&extend=no&hconst=73&omegam=0.27&omegav=0.73&corr_z=1&out_csys=Equatorial&out_equinox=J2000.0&obj_sort=RA+or+Longitude&of=pre_text&zv_breaker=30000.0&list_limit=5&img_stamp=YES |date=20190217081522 }} NASA/IPAC Extragalactic Database</ref>。

